title: "Cursor fingerprints: replace per-command presentation-flag deny-lists with contract-declared semantic classification in sdk/pagination"
description: Declare query-semantic versus presentation-only flags in contracts so SDK cursor fingerprints stay stable without per-command deny-list maintenance.
